casebody.data:
Tuesday, November 6, 2001

MOTION DOCKET

85-1616. State v. Brooks.

Cuyahoga App. No. 48914. Upon consideration of appellee’s motion to set execution date,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to set execution date be, and the same is hereby, denied.

IT IS FURTHER ORDERED that counsel for the appellant and for the appellee shall notify this court within thirty days of completion of federal proceedings.
